Sentencas: Novel atomic layer deposition (ALD) process to deposit high-quality SrCoO3-delta thin films is introduced.
Titulo: SrCoO3-δ thin films by atomic layer deposition

Sentencas: Linear film growth is demonstrated within the film-thickness range of 15-300 nm.
Titulo: SrCoO3-δ thin films by atomic layer deposition

Sentencas: Post-annealing at 600 degrees C (in 02 or N2 atmosphere) is required to crystallize the as-deposited amorphous films.
Titulo: SrCoO3-δ thin films by atomic layer deposition

Sentencas: The new ALD process produces SrCoO3-delta films with a precisely controlled cation stoichiometry (+/- 2.5%) and an appreciably high growth rate (1.67A per supercycle), hence providing us with a prominent method of fabricating high-quality SrCoO3-delta thin films in a readily scalable manner e.g. for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cell cathodes.
Titulo: SrCoO3-δ thin films by atomic layer deposition
